snippet.title: 36200 iOS/Android Gameplay
snippet.description:
A match3 BUT this one will give a different play style you never play before.
----------------
A match3 game with unique gameplay, beautiful background and many hidden achievement wait for you to discover.

You will diving deep into the ocean through the game to discover the ocean and sea creatures.

Key Features

- Pick and move anywhere to match as many as as possible until the air gauge run out.

- Try to maintain the air while match the diving technique to diving as deep as possible.

- Unlock many achievements through the gameplay, many hidden wait for you to find.

- Challenge your friend through the leaderboard to see who diving to the deepest and how many hidden achievement you can unlock.

And much more coming out in the next version.

-------
Want to give a try?
